text: Alfred Kucharczyk (born 2 November 1937) is a Polish gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wodzisław County
